date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWere it not a burden upon my nation, I would have ordered them to use the toothstick before every prayer.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"I would have ordered them to use the toothstick with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33108,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/siwak-after-qiyam-al-layl\/","url_meta":{"origin":18516,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Miswak: The Prophet brushes his teeth after night prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray at night in cycles two by two, then he used the toothstick after he finished. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 288 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33106,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/first-thing-prophet-does\/","url_meta":{"origin":18516,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: First thing the Prophet does at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Shurayh reported: I asked Aisha, saying, \u201cWhat was the first thing the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, did when he entered his house?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cUse the toothstick.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 253 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062d\u064d \u0633\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064f\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0623\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/prophet-asks-nur-noor\/","url_meta":{"origin":18516,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet asks Allah for light in his heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: He spent the night with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he woke up. The Prophet cleansed his teeth, performed ablution, the call to prayer was announced, and he went out for the prayer while he was saying, \u201cO Allah, place light\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18572,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/19\/siwak-clean-please-rabb\/","url_meta":{"origin":18516,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Toothstick cleans mouth, pleases Lord","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe toothstick is cleansing for the mouth and pleasing to the Lord.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 5 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u0650\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0643\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0637\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064c \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0645\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064c \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0651\u0650 5 \u0633\u0646\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0633\u0627\u0626\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33102,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/visit-prophet-bad-oral-hygiene\/","url_meta":{"origin":18516,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Teeth: You visit the Prophet with bad oral hygiene?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Abbas repor